title: Reuters TV Special: The Trump Effect on Davos
text:
Reuters TV Special: The Trump Effect on Davos 6:42pm EST - 18:21 
DAVOS, SWITZERLAND - U.S. President Donald Trump told the crowd in Davos that America is open for business. We’re live in Davos with analysis of his speech, which ranged in topic from the economy to trade and terrorism.
